<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Password Reset - Social Market Place</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 30px auto;
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    header {
      background-color: #fc00ed;
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
    }

    header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
    }

    .body-content {
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .body-content p {
      margin: 15px 0;
      color: #555;
    }

    .reset-token {
      background-color: #fc00ed;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .reset-token p {
      margin: 5px 0;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 15px;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #777;
      border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea;
    }

    .footer a {
      color: #fc00ed;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .footer a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <header>
      <h1>Password Reset - Social Market Place</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="body-content">
      <p>Dear <%= user.name %>,</p>

      <p>We received a request to reset your password for Social Market Place. Please use the token below to proceed:</p>

      <div class="reset-token">
        <p><b>Token:</b> <%= user.token %></p>
        <p><b>Expires In:</b> 10 minutes</p>
      </div>

      <p>If you did not request this reset, please ignore this email or contact our support team immediately.</p>

      <p>Best regards,</p>
      <p>Social Market Place Team</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>This email was sent from <b>Social Market Place</b>. If you have any questions, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@socialmarketplace.com">support@socialmarketplace.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>
